FBIS4-19687 "drweu077_q_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-077 Daily Report 20 Apr 1994 TURKEY Cross-Border Operation Into Iraq Continues Cross-Border Operation Into Iraq Continues TA2004184094 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1648 GMT 20 Apr 94 TA2004184094 Ankara TRT Television Network Turkish BFN [Announcer-read report over video] [Excerpt] The cross-border operation, which was launched by the Turkish Armed Forces in northern Iraq on 12 April, is continuing. During searches conducted in a total of 200 shelters belonging to the terrorist organization in the Mezi, (Kergaderi), and Shiva camps, security forces seized numerous weapons and ammunition as well as large quantities of food and clothing. The caves and shelters, which were uncovered by the security forces, are being destroyed. Meanwhile, following operations conducted in Gabar Mountain in Sirnak, security forces are continuing their search and comb operations in the region. [passage omitted]
